reviewText: This is not even a 480 quality of video.  I can't even see Beyonce.  If I had 20 20 vision I still couldn't tell who the f is in the video.  At first I thought my eye sight was going bad but that was not the case.  All I can tell is the sound of Beyonce.  This is by far the worst quality I have ever seen.  I recommend not to buy this item.  You will be better off getting it from an apple store online then converting the media to be able to play anywhere.  Definitely not worth what I spent.
